Description: Distiller MCP Hub - Hardware Control Services
 A comprehensive Model Context Protocol (MCP) server hub that provides
 hardware control services for the Distiller CM5 platform.
 .
 This package includes:
  * Camera MCP Service - Pi Camera control and image capture
  * Microphone MCP Service - Audio recording and transcription
  * Speaker MCP Service - Text-to-speech using Piper TTS
  * MCP Hub Manager - Orchestrates all services
  * systemd integration for automatic startup
 .
 The services provide HTTP/SSE APIs for hardware control and can be
 integrated with MCP-compatible clients like Claude Desktop.
 .
 Python dependencies are managed using uv package manager with
 per-project virtual environments using Python. 
